snippet.title: Super WEIRD & CUTE ANIMAL FRIENDSHIPS - I BET you will LAUGH FOR HOURS
snippet.description:
These videos are so super cute and hilarious! Look at all these weird and funny animal friendships. Did you know that cats, dogs, pigs, ducks, ferrets, rabbits,..  can be such good friends? So ridiculous, funny and cute! This is a super hard try not to laugh challenge! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
